name: GameTickListener
description: Fires an event on each game tick processed

methods.name: onGameTick
methods.description: onGameTick @Deprecated default void onGameTick() Deprecated. see onServerTick() instead Fires one game cycle after npcs are updated

methods.name: onPreTick
methods.description: onPreTick default void onPreTick() Fires once before npcs are updated every game tick

methods.name: onServerTick
methods.description: onServerTick default void onServerTick() Fires on cycle following server tick packet, signifies a tick being fully processed
